Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}まるで御伽の話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.51,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}終わり迎えた証
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.22,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}長過ぎる旅路から
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}切り出した一節
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}それはかつてこの地に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}影を落とした悪を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}打ち取りし勇者との
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}短い旅の記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.03,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}物語は終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}勇者は眠りにつく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.21,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}穏やかな日常を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}この地に残して
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.25,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}時の流れは無情に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}人を忘れさせる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}そこに生きた軌跡も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}錆びついていく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}されでも君の
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.14,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}言葉も願いも勇気も
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:28.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今も確かに私の中で
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}生きている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.85,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}同じ途を選んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}それだけだったはずなのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}いつの間にかどうして
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:41.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}頬を伝う涙の理由をもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.24,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}知りたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.28,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}今更だって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.70,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}共に歩んだ旅路をたどれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.16,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}そこに君はいなくとも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}きっと見つけられる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.17,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}宛如童话故事一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.51,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}也是迎来结局的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:41.22,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}是从这漫长的旅途中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:42.93,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}抽离出的一节故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:45.43,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}那是曾令这片土地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.81,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}笼罩上阴霾的邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.81,0:02:50.31,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}是与将其讨伐的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.40,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}短暂旅途的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.03,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}故事已经完结
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.33,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}勇者也已长眠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.21,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}只有这平静的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:11.79,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}留在这片土地上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.25,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}时间无情地流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.59,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}人们也终将忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:19.42,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}就连生活过的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.13,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}也终将被锈蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.76,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}纵使如此你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.14,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}言语 心愿 勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:28.39,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}如今也仍在我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:30.52,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}熠熠生辉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.27,0:03:32.85,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}选择了同样的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.02,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}明明只是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.61,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}却为何在不知不觉中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:41.11,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}泪水会从脸庞上划过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.24,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我想明白其中的缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.28,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}即便是事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.28,0:03:45.70,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}但要是能再踏上那条路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:49.16,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}即便你已不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.12,OPCH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}也一定能找到
